videos.description: On their first play from scrimmage, Northern Illinois running back Jordan Huff breaks off a 31-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Huff starts game with TD

videos.description: Western Michigan quarterback Reece Goddard throws a touchdown to Keishawn Watson that evens the score at 7-7.
videos.headline: Goddard tosses TD for Broncos

videos.description: Marcus Childers walks into the end zone on a quarterback draw for a Northern Illinois touchdown.
videos.headline: Childers' 1-yard TD

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin gets in the end zone from 2 yards out for another Broncos touchdown.
videos.headline: Franklin punches in TD

videos.description: Northern Illinois' Sutton Smith picks up the fumble and takes it to the house.
videos.headline: Smith capitalizes on turnover with scoop-and-score

videos.description: Northern Illinois punter Matt Ference's punt goes only 8 yards after wind stops it.
videos.headline: Wind dominates Northern Illinois punt

videos.description: Reece Goddard scrambles for a 7-yard Western Michigan touchdown to tie the game at 21
videos.headline: Goddard scrambles for TD

videos.description: Donnie Ernsberger takes the Reece Goddard  pass 13 yards for a Western Michigan touchdown.
videos.headline: Ernsberger dives for TD

videos.description: Jordan Huff evens the score at 28 with a 13-yard touchdown run in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Huff's 13-yard TD

videos.description: Reece Goddard throws to a wide-open Tyron Arnett who puts the Broncos into the red zone.
videos.headline: Goddard hits Arnett for 68-yard completion

videos.description: Mitchell Brinkman takes the Marcus Childers pass to the house and gives the Huskies the lead.
videos.headline: Brinkman grabs 26-yard TD

videos.description: Throughout Tuesday's Northern Illinois-Western Michigan game, the ball would fall off the tee and a punt attempt goes horribly awry.
